statements: SELECT * FROM PrintingProgress;
SELECT job_id, job_name FROM PrintingProgress;
SELECT job_name, pages_printed FROM PrintingProgress WHERE pages_printed > 100;
SELECT * FROM PrintingProgress WHERE start_time >= '2022-09-01';
SELECT job_id, total_pages FROM PrintingProgress WHERE end_time IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM PrintingProgress WHERE pages_printed > 100 ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT job_name, total_pages FROM PrintingProgress WHERE total_pages < 200 ORDER BY job_name ASC;
SELECT job_id, start_time, end_time FROM PrintingProgress WHERE end_time IS NOT NULL ORDER BY job_id DESC;
SELECT job_name, total_pages FROM PrintingProgress WHERE job_name LIKE '%Invoice%' AND pages_printed = total_pages;
SELECT job_id, job_name, pages_printed, total_pages, start_time, end_time FROM PrintingProgress WHERE pages_printed > 50 AND end_time > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY job_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM job_progress;
SELECT job_name, progress_status, start_time FROM job_progress WHERE job_id = 1;
SELECT job_id, job_name FROM job_progress WHERE progress_status = 'COMPLETE';
SELECT * FROM print_logs ORDER BY log_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT log_id, log_message FROM print_logs WHERE job_id = 2 ORDER BY log_timestamp ASC;
SELECT job_name, progress_status FROM job_progress WHERE job_id = 100
SELECT log_id, log_message FROM print_logs WHERE log_timestamp > '2021-09-01' ORDER BY log_timestamp DESC
SELECT * FROM job_progress WHERE progress_status = 'completed' AND start_time BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31'
SELECT job_name, log_message FROM job_progress INNER JOIN print_logs ON job_progress.job_id = print_logs.job_id
SELECT job_id, COUNT(log_id) AS log_count FROM print_logs GROUP BY job_id HAVING log_count > 5 ORDER BY log_count DESC
SELECT * FROM print_jobs;
SELECT job_id, job_name, progress, timestamp FROM print_jobs;
SELECT job_name, progress FROM print_jobs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM job_history WHERE status = 'completed';
SELECT user_name, timestamp FROM job_users ORDER BY user_name ASC, timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM print_jobs WHERE progress > 50 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT job_id, job_name, timestamp FROM print_jobs WHERE progress < 50 ORDER BY job_name ASC;
SELECT job_name, progress, EXTRACT(DAY FROM timestamp) AS day FROM print_jobs WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM timestamp) = 5;
SELECT j.job_name, j.progress, u.user_name, j.timestamp AS job_timestamp FROM print_jobs j JOIN job_users u ON j.job_id = u.job_id ORDER BY u.user_name, j.timestamp DESC;
SELECT j.job_name, j.progress, h.status, h.history_timestamp FROM print_jobs j JOIN job_history h ON j.job_id = h.job_id WHERE h.history_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT id, job_name, progress, timestamp FROM JobProgress;
SELECT status, timestamp, printer_id FROM PrinterStatus ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT job_id, status FROM JobHistory WHERE status = 'completed';
SELECT * FROM PrintQueue WHERE position < 10 ORDER BY position ASC;
SELECT job_name, progress FROM JobProgress WHERE progress > 50;
SELECT * FROM JobProgress WHERE progress > 50 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT job_name, progress FROM JobProgress WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01' ORDER BY progress DESC;
SELECT J.job_name, P.status, Q.position FROM JobProgress J JOIN PrinterStatus P ON J.id = P.printer_id JOIN PrintQueue Q ON J.id = Q.job_id WHERE P.status = 'Ready' ORDER BY Q.position ASC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT job_id) AS total_jobs, AVG(progress) AS average_progress FROM JobProgress WHERE timestamp >= '2022-03-01';
SELECT J.job_name, H.status AS last_status FROM JobProgress J JOIN JobHistory H ON J.id = H.job_id WHERE J.progress = (SELECT MAX(progress) FROM JobProgress);
SELECT * FROM job_progress;
SELECT job_id, progress FROM job_progress WHERE job_id = 100;
SELECT * FROM job_details ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT job_name, start_time FROM job_details WHERE start_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT printer_id, status FROM printer_status WHERE status = 'offline' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT job_id, progress, timestamp FROM job_progress WHERE progress='completed';
SELECT job_id, progress, timestamp FROM job_progress ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT job_name, start_time, end_time FROM job_details WHERE start_time >= '2022-01-01' AND end_time < '2022-02-01';
SELECT printer_id, status, timestamp FROM printer_status WHERE status='offline' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT job_id, printer_id, start_time, end_time FROM job_printer_mapping WHERE printer_id=1 AND start_time >= '2022-03-01' ORDER BY start_time DESC;
